Properties.Name: Users
Properties.Comment: APK:413 - # 744.2.1.1 it is Acceptable not to disable the selection history, since it is used, and the selection redefinition is fixed, that is, service and invalid users will not get into it, but if they somehow got into it, this is not a problem

v8:item.v8:content: The user presentation in the interface. Usually, first name + last name.
The user does not have access to the application but their data is still stored. Inactive users are hidden from the user lists.
The individual that owns the user account.
Utility user intended for app automation. Its rights cannot be configured interactively.
The user has been submitted for authorization.
The infobase user UUID that is used to map the catalog item to the infobase user.
The service user UUID that is used to map the catalog item to the service user.
The internal storage of some infobase user properties.
Text of the additional String attribute.
Contact information (such as addresses, web pages, or phone numbers).
The contact information type (such as address or phone).
Contact information presentation to display in forms.
The country is required for the address.
The state is required for the address.
The city is required for the address.
The domain of an email server or a web page.
Phone number without area codes and extension
The contact information kind to display in the list.
